@startuml
title Signup and Verify Flow
actor User
participant Frontend
participant Backend
database DB

User -> Frontend: Fill signup form (email/phone, password, referral)
Frontend -> Backend: POST /api/users/signup
Backend -> DB: Create User record with OTP and expiry
Backend -> Frontend: Return OTP (for demo)

User -> Frontend: Enter OTP
Frontend -> Backend: POST /api/users/verify
Backend -> DB: Find user by email, validate OTP and expiry
Backend -> DB: Set IsVerified = true
Backend -> Frontend: 200 OK
@enduml
